title: Documentation - Glossary words ignored by Translation
abstract:
# Documentation - Glossary words ignored by Translation
When you use a glossary for a translation, Cloud Translation ignores the following stopwords that are in your glossary. A glossary entry is ignored only if the entry exactly matches a stopword. For example, the glossary entry `when` is ignored, but the entry `when and what` is not.
